    <owl:NamedIndividual rdf:about="https://w3id.org/rockworx/acq/transform#DASReform2025">
        <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/rockworx/acq/transform#DefenseAcquisitionSystemReform"/>
        <obo:BFO_0000057 rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/rockworx/acq/transform#reorganizedProgramExecutiveOffices"/>
        <rdfs:comment>Temporally bounded 2025-present; directed by Executive Order 14265, &apos;Modernizing Defense Acquisitions and Spurring Innovation in the Defense Industrial Base&apos; (9 April 2025) -- the directing instrument, implemented later in 2025 by the Secretary of War memorandum transforming the DAS into the WAS.</rdfs:comment>
