        <obo:IAO_0000115>A funding source that is the CAPE-maintained (Cost Assessment and Program Evaluation) reserve established to address the valley of death between prototype demonstration and program of record funding.</obo:IAO_0000115>
        <rdfs:isDefinedBy rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/rockworx/acq/transform"/>
