    <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/rockworx/acq/transform#JointForceRequirementsProcess">
        <obo:IAO_0000115>A planned process that is the Joint Force Requirements Process (JFRP) that replaced JCIDS; under it the re-oriented Joint Requirements Oversight Council (JROC) ranks Key Operational Problems rather than validating prescriptive capability documents.</obo:IAO_0000115>
        <rdfs:isDefinedBy rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/rockworx/acq/transform"/>
